title: Prosthetic limbs expert to lead engineering science at Greenwich (University of Greenwich)
text: ( Source : University of Greenwich ) A leading expert in prosthetic limbs has joined the University of Greenwich as its Head of Engineering Science . Professor Peter Kyberd has a wealth of experience in designing, programming and testing
